title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland-Alameda County Coliseum on 1987-12-27
lineage: MAC > Nakamichi DR-2 > Edirol FA-66 > Wavelab > TLH > FLAC 2448 tagged. Transfer by Andrew F. 06/2012
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Gray, Jack Straw, Peggy-O, Walkin' Blues, Ramble On Rose, Me & My Uncle-> Big River, It Must Have Been The Roses, Desolation Row, Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Playin' In The Band-> Uncle John's Band-> Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> Jam-> Dear Mr. Fantasy-> Stella Blue-> Throwing Stones-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: The Mighty Quinn
